OL,4,CBury pub landlord catches Lee Rigby
OL,5,Ccollection box thief
OL,6, A thief who tried to steal a Lee Rigby
OL,7, Foundation charity box from a pub was
OL,8, caught by the landlord - one of the
OL,9, soldier's former comrades.
OL,11,FStewart Spensley, landlord of The Two
OL,12,FTubs in Bury, gave chase after the
OL,13,Fdonation box was taken from the bar.
OL,15,FFusilier Rigby was killed outside
OL,16,FWoolwich Barracks in south-east London
OL,17,Fin May 2013 in a terror-related attack.
OL,19,FMr Spensley, 42, who served three tours
OL,20,Fof Afghanistan, said: "I was not going
OL,21,Fto let it go."
